    "title": "Given the choice between two speeding cars, which will a cop pull over? For instance, let's say I'm driving through a 45 mph speed zone going 48 mph driving next to another car going 54 mph. Who does he pull over, if at all? - Quora",
    "tags": [
        "Speeding Tickets",
        "Traffic Tickets"
