            "answer_text": "I was driving upstate NY, there were somewhat traffic but moving nicely, most of people were doing 75+ on the 65 mph highway, i was going about the same as most of the cars, listening to the radio and going about my business, then all of the sudden i see lights behind me. Damn, what the hell happen here, i was a bit confused, the cop was polite telling me i was doing i believe 78 in 65, i told him i was going with the traffic and everyone around me was going about the same speed or even a bit more for a few, and his response was, well maybe, but i can only stop one car at the time.. I guess it was my lucky day.. But in your case i depends what the cop is doing, i\u2019m sure he will go for the one going 54, unless he had used the laser gun on the one doing 48 mph.. So its mostly random, unless the other car speed is significantly higher.. ",
